        "rendered": "<p>Go back to the list of Blocks Use the Row block to arrange blocks horizontally.&nbsp;&nbsp; Click the (+) icon to open the block inserter pop-up window and search for the Row block. You can also use the keyboard shortcut /row-block to quickly insert a Row block. Detailed instructions on adding blocks can be found here. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
